  <thing id="cMPSGGDITT" name="Done It A Thousand Times" description="The escapist is used to performing dangerous and difficult stunts for the entertainment of others, and can draw on that experience whenever she&apos;s calm enough. \n\nWhenever the escapist &quot;takes 10&quot; on a skill, she receives a +2 circumstance bonus to the total skill check.\n\nFor each Hero Point spent, the escapist gains an additional stacking +2 circumstance bonus to the total skill check." compset="CustomSpec" summary="&quot;takes 10&quot; on a skill, she receives a +2 bonus" uniqueness="useronce">
