  <thing id="cMPSGGAdR1" name="Adrenaline Rush (SGG)" description="After constantly putting her body through stressful moments that cause her adrenaline to flow freely, the escapist has learned to call upon a powerful rush on command. The escapist can temporarily increase one of her physical ability scores (Strength, Dexterity, or Constitution). The escapist increases the selected ability score by 1d4+1 points and the bonus lasts for a number of rounds equal to her class level. At the end of the duration, the escapist is fatigued for 1d6 x 10 minutes. \n\nAn escapist cannot use her adrenaline rush if she is fatigued or exhausted.\n\nFor each Hero Point spent, the escapist can temporarily increase an additional physical ability scores." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Temporarily increase one of her physical ability scores" uniqueness="useronce">
    <comment>Anachronistic Adventurers - The Daredevil

Super Genius Games
www.supergeniusgames.com</comment>
