  <thing id="cMPSGGIUDg" name="Improved Uncanny Dodge" description="The daredevil can no longer be flanked. \n\nThis defense denies a rogue the ability to sneak attack the daredevil by flanking him, unless the attacker has at least four more rogue levels than the target has daredevil levels. \n\nIf a character already has uncanny dodge from another class, the levels from the classes that grant uncanny dodge stack to determine the minimum rogue level required to flank the character. \n\nA daredevil must be at least 10th level and have the uncanny dodge talent in order to select this talent." compset="CustomSpec" summary="The daredevil can no longer be flanked." uniqueness="useronce">
